00:24:14,420 --> 00:24:17,650
An acting Chairman.  But it's almost similar.

268
00:24:17,650 --> 00:24:23,140
Wow, he's amazing. He finally took over this castle.

269
00:24:23,140 --> 00:24:24,080
This castle?

