523
00:45:17,890 --> 00:45:19,270
Thank you.

524
00:45:19,270 --> 00:45:23,980
I'll call Chief Han Jae Joon personally.

525
00:45:29,620 --> 00:45:31,670
The performing surgeon has changed?

526
00:45:31,670 --> 00:45:34,690
Yes, I'm sorry.

527
00:45:34,690 --> 00:45:36,160
It doesn't matter.

528
00:45:36,160 --> 00:45:40,580
Chairman Oh's son will be released soon.

529
00:45:42,210 --> 00:45:45,870
I'm warning you but whatever you do,

530
00:45:45,870 --> 00:45:49,130
