531
00:45:49,130 --> 00:45:53,750
When the surgery is done, I will give you a chance to take care of Oh Joon Gyu,

532
00:45:53,750 --> 00:45:57,710
so stay quiet until then, understand?

533
00:46:36,300 --> 00:46:40,150
This tiresome work will be over in a week, too.

534
00:47:02,530 --> 00:47:03,920
Are you here?

535
00:47:03,920 --> 00:47:05,090
Where's my mom?

536
00:47:05,090 --> 00:47:08,980
We're taking good care of your mother,

537
00:47:08,980 --> 00:47:10,800
so don't worry.

538
00:47:11,700 --> 00:47:15,970
If you just finish the surgery well, she'll be safe.

539
00:47:15,970 --> 00:47:18,610
I don't trust your words anymore.

540
00:47:18,610 --> 00:47:20,500
Fine.

541
00:47:20,500 --> 00:47:23,890
How would it be if I said it like this?

542
00:47:25,660 --> 00:47:30,680
If you say something stupid,

543
00:47:30,680 --> 00:47:34,900
your mother will die.

544
00:47:38,630 --> 00:47:40,640
How's that?

545
00:47:50,750 --> 00:47:54,490
The president chose me as the performing surgeon.

546
00:47:54,490 --> 00:47:56,790
What about your mother?

547
00:47:56,790 --> 00:47:59,200
She'll be fine.

548
00:47:59,200 --> 00:48:03,910
As long as I'm the one performing the surgery, they'll also take good care of her.

549
00:48:06,300 --> 00:48:08,750
What are you going to do now?

550
00:48:08,750 --> 00:48:10,420
It's as I said before.

551
00:48:10,420 --> 00:48:14,430
When the day of the President's surgery comes, you just need to as well as you normally do.

552
00:48:14,430 --> 00:48:16,050
I'll take care of the rest.

553
00:48:16,050 --> 00:48:18,860
