555
00:48:21,670 --> 00:48:26,200
Taking care of that much, I got enough training with Cha Jin Soo for 2 years.

556
00:48:26,200 --> 00:48:27,970
Take care?

557
00:48:27,970 --> 00:48:32,630
Then did you think I came here with just anesthesiology training?

558
00:48:32,630 --> 00:48:34,890
- Why would you-
- You're right.

559
00:48:34,890 --> 00:48:38,400
If I knew that you'd killed my father, I wouldn't have even started getting

560
00:48:38,400 --> 00:48:41,280
that kind of scary training.

561
00:48:42,520 --> 00:48:45,520
Because the will to see you wouldn't have existed.

562
00:48:49,980 --> 00:48:54,710
What are you going to do if everything ends safely as you think?

563
00:48:54,710 --> 00:48:59,140
I don't know. But the one thing I'm sure of

564
00:48:59,140 --> 00:49:02,480
is that I'll never be with you.

565
00:49:17,670 --> 00:49:19,460
If it's about Lee Seung Hoon, I don't want to hear it, so leave!

566
00:49:19,460 --> 00:49:22,040
Even if you don't want to hear it, listen.

567
00:49:26,330 --> 00:49:29,790
That person was adopted to America after the medical accident incident.

568
00:49:29,790 --> 00:49:30,760
Get out!

569
00:49:30,760 --> 00:49:33,170
He came to Korea to take revenge on you.

570
00:49:33,170 --> 00:49:35,100
Why are you uselessly going around meeting that bastard?

571
00:49:35,100 --> 00:49:36,930
You also saw Oppa getting arrested!

572
00:49:36,930 --> 00:49:39,270
That's been taken care of!

573
00:49:39,270 --> 00:49:41,910
Apologize sincerely to that man.

574
00:49:41,910 --> 00:49:43,520
Then he will definitely forgive you.

575
00:49:43,520 --> 00:49:45,960
Apologize?

576
00:49:45,960 --> 00:49:49,120
Impudent fool. I did nothing wrong.

577
00:49:49,160 --> 00:49:51,270
What do you mean you did nothing wrong?

578
00:49:51,270 --> 00:49:55,340
That person's father passed away and because the lawsuit was dropped, he even lost his mother.

579
00:49:55,340 --> 00:49:57,400
Overnight, he became an orphan!

580
00:49:57,400 --> 00:49:59,810
So I'm telling you to seek forgiveness by saying sorry!

581
00:49:59,810 --> 00:50:01,920
Won't you shut up!?

582
00:50:01,920 --> 00:50:06,360
Father, do you really not know what you did wrong?

583
00:50:06,360 --> 00:50:09,850
I said I did nothing wrong!

584
00:50:14,450 --> 00:50:17,430
He dares to mess with me?

585
00:50:17,430 --> 00:50:19,790
Tell him to try as much as he wants!

586
00:50:19,790 --> 00:50:24,200
No matter how much fuss a guy like that makes, I won't fall.

587
00:50:33,340 --> 00:50:35,560
Jae Joon.

588
00:50:37,310 --> 00:50:40,630
I know you used me

589
00:50:40,630 --> 00:50:43,200
and deceived me.

590
00:50:43,200 --> 00:50:48,440
I'll forget everything, so please stop here, Jae Joon.

591
00:50:48,440 --> 00:50:50,550
I'm sorry, Soo Hyeon.

592
00:50:52,200 --> 00:50:54,640
I haven't told Father anything yet.

593
00:50:54,640 --> 00:50:58,620
I'll try to convince him somehow, so stop...

594
00:50:59,480 --> 00:51:01,570
Don't try.

595
00:51:59,400 --> 00:52:02,820
You have something you need to do.

596
00:52:02,820 --> 00:52:04,490
Are you talking about Lee Seung Hoon?

597
00:52:04,490 --> 00:52:05,500
Yes.

598
00:52:05,500 --> 00:52:07,910
I  just came after meeting him.

599
00:52:09,050 --> 00:52:10,910
Really?

600
00:52:12,070 --> 00:52:14,070
What does he want?

601
00:52:14,070 --> 00:52:15,940
How much does he want?

602
00:52:15,940 --> 00:52:18,270
He said he doesn't need money.

603
00:52:19,020 --> 00:52:23,970
Lee Seung Hoon, that bastard, was really tenacious even as a child.

604
00:52:23,970 --> 00:52:28,050
 Don't forget. My father is Lee Jo Seon, and I'm Lee Seung Hoon.

605
00:52:28,050 --> 00:52:29,790
 Remember that clearly!

606
00:52:29,790 --> 00:52:33,700
 I'm telling you to clearly remember the person who's going to take revenge on you!

607
00:52:33,700 --> 00:52:36,220
When it's been 20 years,

608
00:52:36,220 --> 00:52:38,360
to think that he would stab me in the back!

609
00:52:38,360 --> 00:52:43,490
If you'll apologize sincerely even now and acknowledge your wrong, then he said he'll stop the revenge.

610
00:52:43,490 --> 00:52:46,890
Apologize? Acknowledge?

611
00:52:46,890 --> 00:52:49,880
Impudent fool.

612
00:52:49,880 --> 00:52:54,270
I have nothing to apologize for or to acknowledge.

613
00:52:55,050 --> 00:52:57,560
Blocking the medical incident then

614
00:52:57,560 --> 00:53:00,930
was the best thing that I've done.

615
00:53:06,660 --> 00:53:09,280
If the lawsuit had progressed back then,

616
00:53:09,280 --> 00:53:12,650
Myeongwoo would have disintegrated into the air.

617
00:53:12,650 --> 00:53:16,000
You have no thoughts that you did wrong?

618
00:53:16,000 --> 00:53:17,990
Not at all!

619
00:53:17,990 --> 00:53:22,330
I, Oh Joon Gyu, protected Myeongwoo.

620
00:53:22,330 --> 00:53:24,280
No one can touch Myeongwoo!

621
00:53:24,280 --> 00:53:26,950
You never know if Lee Seung Hoon gave you a last chance.

622
00:53:26,950 --> 00:53:28,230
What chance?!

623
00:53:28,230 --> 00:53:33,620
The last chance for not being able to apologize and pleading for forgiveness back then.

624
00:53:33,620 --> 00:53:37,860
The thing the victims of the medical incident want is a sincere apology.

625
00:53:37,860 --> 00:53:41,170
- Even last time...
- Tell him not to make me laugh!

626
00:53:44,210 --> 00:53:46,380
At this rate,

627
00:53:46,380 --> 00:53:48,520
if Lee Seung Hoon decides to do something dangerous...

628
00:53:48,520 --> 00:53:52,010
Tell him to give it a try.

629
00:53:52,010 --> 00:53:54,340
Whether he tries to retaliate or avenge,

630
00:53:54,340 --> 00:53:57,490
no matter how much he desperately tries,

631
00:53:57,490 --> 00:54:01,140
he will never make me fall.

632
00:54:01,140 --> 00:54:02,810
Do you really think that?

633
00:54:02,810 --> 00:54:05,110
Sang Jin's prosecution investigation?

634
00:54:05,110 --> 00:54:07,160
I've blocked it all.

635
00:54:07,160 --> 00:54:11,700
But it seems you won't be able to block what's about to happen now.

636
00:54:11,700 --> 00:54:16,510
The branch hospital that's being built in Jeju Island won't be able to open.

