643
00:54:34,260 --> 00:54:36,290
You already know that he found out about embezzlement of the school foundation's funds

644
00:54:36,290 --> 00:54:40,950
and the corruption of evaluation from Judge Kim Pyeong Woo.

645
00:54:42,210 --> 00:54:47,560
You have to pay up 5 times the unjustified treatment cost that's been claimed as an additional fee.

