00:54:47,560 --> 00:54:50,080
The amount of that sum will be huge.

647
00:54:50,940 --> 00:54:52,900
Lee Seung Hoon.

648
00:54:53,880 --> 00:54:56,430
Lee Seung Hoon, you bastard.

649
00:54:59,360 --> 00:55:05,350
How dare you? You dare to mess with me?!

650
00:55:17,830 --> 00:55:21,590
Find a solution

651
00:55:21,590 --> 00:55:25,210
