652
00:55:26,420 --> 00:55:28,720
It's not over yet.

653
00:55:28,720 --> 00:55:33,030
20 years ago, when Meyongwoo was getting approved as an university hospital,

654
00:55:33,030 --> 00:55:36,790
he said he'll announce the willful close alliance with the politicians.

655
00:55:36,790 --> 00:55:38,210
What?

656
00:55:38,210 --> 00:55:41,920
Prime Minister Jang Seok Joo's name will be the first to come out.

657
00:55:42,830 --> 00:55:47,930
That... bring that bastard Lee Seung Hoon in front of me right now.

658
00:55:47,930 --> 00:55:50,270
Right now!

659
00:55:50,270 --> 00:55:52,410
What happened?

660
00:55:54,640 --> 00:55:58,440
Jae Joon. Jae Joon.

661
00:55:58,440 --> 00:56:01,480
For the last 20 years, he said that he hasn't forgotten for even a day,

662
00:56:01,480 --> 00:56:04,320
